{
  "texts": [
    "In other words, it's not the use of words that leads to higher evaluation, but rather these words are a corollary of some inherent better quality.",
    "Our current analysis can't decipher between those two interpretations but does suggest that the use of these words is meaningful for humans.",
    "The goal of the current paper was to compare humans' and GPT-4's ability to conduct cognitive reappraisal.",
    "Across four studies we found that GPT-4 outperformed humans in the dimensions of effectiveness, empathy, and novelty but not in terms of the specificity of the produced reappraisal to the current context.",
    "In Study 2, we replicated the effects of study 1 in real-time human-EXPLORING HUMAN AND AI EMOTIONAL SUPPORT human and human-AI interactions, with first-person ratings of the reappraisals."
